# Claude Code session artefacts, skills, and any other state the IDE drops
# into this directory — all sourced from the user's global ~/.claude install,
# not meaningful per-project history. Covers session-state.md, error-tracker.json,
# plpgsql-graph.json, plpgsql-graph-report.md, skills/, and anything else the
# harness may add in future.
.claude/

